MR B AND ME
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Although we have only met once Mr B and I have had a long business
    relationship, every Tuesday, Thursday and Saturday, going back
    decades. Our only meeting was about 15 years ago, early one summer
    morning. I was coming home after a night out and he was delivering
    milk. I strolled over and introduced myself and he did the same and
    that was that.

